## Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|
| Auth redirect breaks | Keep `if (isAuthenticated) return null` and `router.push('/dashboard')` unchanged |
| Mobile menu breaks | Keep mobile menu JSX identical, only add visual polish |
| Scroll behavior breaks | Keep `scrolled` state and navbar logic unchanged |
| Animation performance | Use `transform` and `opacity` only (GPU-accelerated), avoid layout thrashing |
| Page size | All additions are CSS/JSX, no images or external assets needed |
| Cross-browser | CSS `@property` for animated borders works in Chrome/Edge; Firefox fallback is static gradient |
| `@property` support | Only Chrome 85+, Edge 85+. For Firefox, the gradient border falls back to static — acceptable degradation |

